OL,3,CThe dad travelling 6,000 miles in
OL,4,Csearch of a life-saving donor
OL,6,FGranada Reports Correspondent Mel
OL,7,FBarham caught up with Pete and his
OL,8,Ffamily before the possibly life
OL,9,Fchanging journey to Macau.
OL,11,FA father-of-two with blood cancer is
OL,12,Ftravelling to the other side of the
OL,13,Fworld in a bid to save his life.
OL,15,FPete McCleave, 45, was told he had
OL,16,Fseven years to live after being
OL,17,Fdiagnosed with myeloma in 2017.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
