OL,3,CThe dad travelling 6,000 miles in
OL,4,Csearch of a life-saving donor
OL,6,FPete's grandmother Lucille Da'Costa
OL,7,Fwas born in Macau, to a Chinese mother
OL,8,Fand a Portuguese father, while his
OL,9,Fgrandfather was from Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FHe is travelling more than 6,000 miles
OL,12,Fto attend Encontro - an event that
OL,13,Fhappens every four years, where
OL,14,FMacanese diaspora return to the
OL,15,Fcountry for a week of cultural
OL,16,Fcelebrations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
