OL,3,CThe dad travelling 6,000 miles in
OL,4,Csearch of a life-saving donor
OL,6,FPete is hoping to encourage people of
OL,7,FMacanese heritage at the event to sign
OL,8,Fup to the donor register - in the hope
OL,9,Fone of them may be the match he needs
OL,10,Fto save his life.
OL,12,FHe launched the campaign 10,000 donors
OL,13,Fto get more donors on the stem cell
OL,14,Fregister, so far more than 108,000
OL,15,Fpotential donors have signed, with 23
OL,16,Flife saving matches have been found -
OL,17,Fbut none of them a match for Pete.
OL,19,F"This trip could literally be life
OL,20,Fextending, it could be that
OL,21,Fimportant," Pete said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
