OL,3,CThe dad travelling 6,000 miles in
OL,4,Csearch of a life-saving donor
OL,6,F"I don't pin all my hopes on it, but
OL,7,Fit's the best chance I will have of
OL,8,Ffinding that potential genetic twin
OL,9,Ffrom that region.
OL,11,F"I am very, very aware that this blend
OL,12,Fof Chinese, Portuguese, Irish and
OL,13,FEnglish is super, super rare.
OL,15,F"But it will genuinely allow me to
OL,16,Fsay, if the worse were to happen, I
OL,17,Fdid everything I possibly could do."
OL,19,FDespite travelling half way around the
OL,20,Fworld, Pete says he remains realistic,
OL,21,Fbut it was something he had to do.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
