OL,3,CThe dad travelling 6,000 miles in
OL,4,Csearch of a life-saving donor
OL,6,F"I'm honest with myself about the
OL,7,Fchances," he added.
OL,9,F"But if I didn't do it, if I didn't
OL,10,Ftake advantage of this opportunity,
OL,11,Fthis literally once every four years
OL,12,Fget together of people, I don't think
OL,13,FI could look at myself or my family
OL,14,Fand say I did everything that I
OL,15,Fpossibly could to try and bridge that
OL,16,Fgap.
OL,18,F"And I think that's what makes it
OL,19,Fworth trying.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
