OL,3,CThe dad travelling 6,000 miles in
OL,4,Csearch of a life-saving donor
OL,6,F"And it will also help me to
OL,7,Fgenuinely, were the worse to happen,
OL,8,Fmake peace with that moment and say I
OL,9,Fdid everything I could do."
OL,11,FHe continued: "It's time, you can't
OL,12,Fput a price on time. Everyone has
OL,13,Ftheir reason for fighting for
OL,14,Fsomething, and my family is my reason."
OL,16,FPete's cause first came to the
OL,17,Fpublic's attention after his, then
OL,18,Feight-year-old, son Max wrote a letter
OL,19,Fpleading for others to join the stem
OL,20,Fcell registry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
